<view class="container">
  <view class="section">
    <view class="section-title">选择充值套餐</view>
    <view class="package-grid">
      <view
        class="package-item {{selectedPackage === item.id ? 'active' : ''}}"
        wx:for="{{packages}}"
        wx:key="id"
        bindtap="selectPackage"
        data-id="{{item.id}}"
      >
        <view class="package-coins">{{item.coins}} 金币</view>
        <view class="package-bonus" wx:if="{{item.bonus > 0}}">+{{item.bonus}} 赠送</view>
        <view class="package-price">¥{{item.amount}}</view>
      </view>
    </view>
  </view>

  <view class="notice">
    <view class="notice-title">充值说明</view>
    <view class="notice-item">1. 金币充值后不可退款</view>
    <view class="notice-item">2. 金币可用于场馆预约、教练预约、在线点餐等消费</view>
    <view class="notice-item">3. 充值套餐金额越大，赠送金币越多</view>
    <view class="notice-item">4. 如有问题，请联系客服</view>
  </view>

  <view class="bottom-bar">
    <button
      class="btn-recharge"
      bindtap="confirmRecharge"
      loading="{{loading}}"
      disabled="{{loading || !selectedPackage}}"
    >
      {{selectedPackage ? '确认充值' : '请选择套餐'}}
    </button>
  </view>
</view>
